*Uhapšen* je nekoliko ljudi zbog krijumčarenja droge. (Several people were arrested for drug trafficking.)

Nakon što je policija primetila nerede, *uhapšena* su tri lica. (After the police noticed riots, three people were arrested.)

*Uhapšen* je čovek koji je pokušao da ukrade automobil. (The man who attempted to steal a car was arrested.)

Izbeglice koje su državljani drugih država su *uhapšeni* i deportovani. (The refugees who were citizens of other countries were arrested and deported.)

*Uhapšen* je optuženi za ubistvo. (The accused of murder was arrested.)